Dialogue: 0,1:45:05.29,1:45:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,都这样了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:12.27,1:45:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,忍耐不住了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:15.94,1:45:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,忍耐不住了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:47.50,1:45:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你懂的吧 没错
Dialogue: 0,1:46:15.76,1:46:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 没错
